{"tid":674773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肚痛5小時痾出嬰屍 湖南15歲媽媽:以為變胖了","createTime":"2018-05-23T04:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T05:55:18.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c45c85026a0994235cbf846b77375a49f715993b","tid":674773,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"湖南一名年僅15歲的少女小惠（化名）本月14日在住所內突然覺得肚子痛，去洗手間時竟痾了一團毛茸茸的東西出來，送到醫院後才知道原來是已死去的嬰兒。<br />\n<br />\n湖南省衡陽市的小惠是由爺爺奶奶帶大，雙親在她6歲時就離婚，讀完中學就到長沙打工。14日下午2點多，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>她一個人在家中時突然覺得肚痛，起初以為是吃錯東西，沒太在意。到了晚上7點多，她到洗手間「解決」，下體突然掉出一團「東西」，而且還是毛茸茸的</strong></span>，她嚇得馬上打電話向朋友求救，最後才在朋友的建議下趕忙叫救護車前往醫院。<br />\n<br />\n原來這團「東西」是一名初生嬰兒，但由於卡在陰道內長達5個小時，出生時就已經死亡了。而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>小惠在懷孕期間除了腹部增大外，並沒有其他不適的症狀</strong></span>。她接受當地傳媒採訪時表示，「我也不知道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上個月只是感覺肚子裡有東西在動，還以為是自己變胖了。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n當地婦產科醫生指出，小惠年紀輕輕，對性知識瞭解太少也缺乏自我保護意識，才會連自己懷孕了都不知道，最後導致悲劇發生。"},{"pid":"b68647169da408779351786ef3bc3c2e5974910e","tid":674773,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be1db5ec03edb6dbfaa02e3354b86093e61e49d8","tid":674773,"uid":63588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"小惠是由爺爺奶奶帶大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd1bc08b3be182ac816d9b99aca26a91d953fd3","tid":674773,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:13:01.000Z","msg":"中出嗰個就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81e9dc515a5550dfbb3cfc8d894ad605c50a6f0","tid":674773,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd1bc08b3be182ac816d9b99aca26a91d953fd3","tid":674773,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:13:01.000Z","msg":"中出嗰個就正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a894ed195b4e5f33b472c8f7e5246c192f9759a1","tid":674773,"uid":4575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be1db5ec03edb6dbfaa02e3354b86093e61e49d8","tid":674773,"uid":63588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"小惠是由爺爺奶奶帶大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"喜歡你既思路"},{"pid":"810980533f602cb26ff6f0616c11fcb272f1aaf9","tid":674773,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"十五歲打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0932f3ac4619119d61ad5e2434b98ed659ce694","tid":674773,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"嬰屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}